name: Sacred Heart and Roses.
description:
Beautiful Sacred Heart flanked by two roses.

The scroll on this lively items can be personalised with a name or short phrase of your choice, or you can choose one of our preset phrases!

Also available without the roses.

This comes on a 16" silver plated chain. Longer lengths available upon request.

Please let me know what you would like for custom lettering in the Notes to Seller part of PayPal.

This would make a great gift for a friend,loved one or for yourself!


*These items are made entirely by hand. As such, they take time,care and attention. Please allow at least 10 working days for your item to be completed before it is sent.

name: Gift Vouchers
description:
Have a friend or loved one who you know would love an item from us but you arent sure what to get?
